<blockquote class="uncited"><div>What is "po2"?</div></blockquote>It is short for power of 2 (2^N). Old graphic cards or drivers have problems handling images not of such a width or height. It can be solved by padding the image.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://love2d.org/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=436">Robin</a> — Wed Mar 24, 2010 6:43 pm</p><hr />
